Crescent was first listed as a [[census designated place]] in the [[2010 U.S. census]].<ref name=2010CensusLA>{{Cite web|title= 2010 Census of Population - Population and Housing Unit Counts - Louisiana |url=https://www2.census.gov/library/publications/decennial/2010/cph-2/cph-2-20.pdf|website=[[United States Census Bureau]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240402175429/https://www2.census.gov/library/publications/decennial/2010/cph-2/cph-2-20.pdf| archive-date=April 2, 2024}}</ref> Its population was 959 at the [[2010 United States Census|2010 census]],<ref name="LA">{{cite web|title=2010 Census Gazetteer Files - Places: Louisiana|url=http://www2.census.gov/geo/docs/maps-data/data/gazetteer/2010_place_list_22.txt|publisher=[[U.S. Census Bureau]]|accessdate=January 16, 2017}}</ref> and by 2020, its population declined to 811.<ref name=":0" />

